      "sc:description": "PyFasma is an open-source Python package for preprocessing and multivariate analysis of Raman spectroscopy data. It offers a modular framework for data processing, dimensionality reduction, and spectral deconvolution, facilitating reproducible and robust analysis of biological samples.",
